Jack Scalia https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Scalia 0 Jack Scalia (born November 10, 1950) is an American actor. He has had many roles in television series (both as a regular and as a guest-star), television movies, and feature films. He is perhaps best known for his role as Chris Stamp on All My Children from 2001 to 2003. Jack_Scalia ( born November_10_,_1950 ) is an_American_actor .
